description: Walk About Pet, WA20008, Super Premium Freeze-Dried Cat Treats, Grain-Free, Gluten-Free, Single Source Protein, Wild Boar, Resealable Pouch, 2-Ounces. Feed your kitty’s wild side with a delicious treat they’ll love from a single all-natural ingredient you can trust. Crafted from single source, freeze-dried Wild Boar as the only ingredient with all it’s potent, natural nutrients intact…exactly the way your cat’s ancestors would’ve eaten in the wild. Proudly made in the USA, we carefully remove only the water leaving the raw nutrients, aroma, flavor, texture and freshness your cat craves. Suitable for adult cats of any breed, these treats provide natural antioxidants, essential vitamins, minerals and high-quality, easily digestible protein for lean muscles. Packed in a resealable pouch to help maintain freshness, there are zero chemicals, preservatives or additives. Grain and gluten-free, single source protein that’s perfect for cats with grain or food sensitivities, allergies or on restricted/limited ingredient diets. Wild Boar is low in saturated fat and cholesterol and has more protein per pound than beef, lamb and chicken. It’s darker meat than domesticated pig with a strong meaty taste and smell that’s perfect for fussy dogs. Wild Boar is considered a "cooling" meat which helps with inflammation. A notable source of Thiamine, B6, Niacin, Zinc and Selenium all of which are essential for energy regulation, carbohydrate metabolism, enzyme function, glucose generation, RBC and nervous system function. Approximately 230 treats per bag; not meant for human consumption. Feeding instructions: use as a snack to supplement your cat’s regular daily feedings.
